{"name": "odoo14-addon-connector-importer-product", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-connector-importer-product", "version": "14.0.2.3.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/connector-interfaces", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-connector-importer", "odoo"], "summary": "Ease definition of product imports using `connector_importer`.", "upload_time": 1685970504}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Alpha-red.png\n    :alt: Alpha\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fconnector--interfaces-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/connector-interfaces\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/connector-interfaces/tree/14.0/connector_importer_product\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/connector-interfaces-14-0/connector-interfaces-14-0-connector_importer_product\n    ```\n  maintainer-mmequignon: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/mmequignon.png?size=40px\n    :alt: mmequignon\n    :target: https://github.com/mmequignon\n    ```\n  maintainer-sebalix: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/sebalix.png?size=40px\n    :alt: sebalix\n    :target: https://github.com/sebalix\n    ```\n  maintainer-simahawk: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/simahawk.png?size=40px\n    :alt: simahawk\n    :target: https://github.com/simahawk\n    ```\n---\n\n# Connector Importer Product\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }}\n\nEase definition of product imports using `connector_importer`.\n\nSupported imports:\n\n- products\n- product attributes\n- product attribute values\n- product categories\n- product packaging\n- product supplier info\n\n:::{IMPORTANT}\nThis is an alpha version, the data model and design can change at any time without warning.\nOnly for development or testing purpose, do not use in production.\n[More details on development status](https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status)\n:::\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\n- get rid of supplier info specific importer\n- find a flexible way to define matching products\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/connector-interfaces/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/connector-interfaces/issues/new?body=module:%20connector_importer_product%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Simone Orsi \\<<mailto:simahawk@gmail.com>>\n- S\u00e9bastien Alix \\<<mailto:sebastien.alix@camptocamp.com>>\n- Jacques-Etienne Baudoux \\<<mailto:je@bcim.be>>\n- Matthieu M\u00e9quignon \\<<mailto:matthieu.mequignon@camptocamp.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainers](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-simahawk }} {{ maintainer-sebalix }} {{ maintainer-mmequignon }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/connector-interfaces](https://github.com/OCA/connector-interfaces/tree/14.0/connector_importer_product) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests.test_product_attribute", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests..test_product_attribute", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests.test_product_category", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests..test_product_category", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests.test_product_packaging", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests..test_product_packaging", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests.test_product_product", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests..test_product_product", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests.test_record_handler", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests..test_record_handler", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.connector_importer_product.tests.common", "documentation": ["Copyright 2022 Camptocamp SA", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)"], "functions": [],